---
title: Afghan Red Lentil Soup with Cumin, Mint, and Lemon
description: In this Afghan-inspired soup, pungent herbs and spices elevate humble lentils to new heights. The combination of both dried and fresh mint highlights different qualities of the same ingredient. Relax, curl up, and enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/55b91feeae92708e3a8b456a.jpg
